        <p>Consent form, case history, physical examination, treatment plan discussion. 45–60 minutes. Gentle hands-on treatment including balanced ligamentous tension, soft tissue techniques, and myofascial unwinding.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="profile-step">
      <span class="profile-step-number">02</span>
      <div>
        <h3>Follow-up Treatments</h3>
        <p>Tailored to your response. May include different osteopathic techniques, dry needling, auricular/electrical acupuncture, and cupping based on progress.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="profile-step">
      <span class="profile-step-number">03</span>
